WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Captain! Captain!

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Is the airship safe?

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Captain, there's only one more station.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Please help us.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
What about the Mirara?

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.000
What about the Chiyu?

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Hurry up and go to the airship!

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Protect the airship with your life!

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
It's a raid!

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:26.000
What?

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Captain!

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Captain!

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.000
They're all fighting on the ship!

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Hey, Nonshi!

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.000
We're going to be friends!

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.000
That's right!

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.000
We're going to be friends!

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Kill the enemy on the ship!

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:53.000
What are you doing?

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Take the bullets and shoot them!

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.000
We'll set the ship on fire!

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
I'll take the role!

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:01.000
You take the role!

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Kill the enemy!

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.000
Nobuchi, shoot them!

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Turn the gun to the left!

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.000
It's a trap!

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.000
I see smoke!

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Shoot them all!

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:21.000
What's going on?

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
I'll take the role!

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.000
I'll take the role!

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.000
The enemy is coming!

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
Kill them!

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.000
What about the captain?

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:44.000
He's dead.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.000
The airship is coming!

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.000
The enemy is coming!

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:53.000
We're going to destroy the ship!

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.000
It's all right now!

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.000
Shoot them!

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Attack!

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:21.000
Prepare to be shot!

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:23.000
Shoot them!

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Shoot them!

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:41.000
Shoot them!

